  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d659aa9d-a9ff-4046-8f9b-106cadd76e8c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a747b353-a4b2-48f9-a6e7-bacb1916d98d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f89d57a9-e0bc-4fce-b635-655276ab1c93\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(보험) 프로필명함 진행과정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-22c9718f-3c64-4776-b17b-98c87fba814e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-7796e79c-a82b-4dfb-b814-5b51db7183aa\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-03da0c92-6384-4323-b072-f96d5a2437f7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프로필명함은 주로 영업을 하시는 분들이 많이 주문하고 계십니다. 대표적인 영업 직군으로는 보험이 있겠습니다. 오늘 주문건에 대해 소개해 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-87bf8769-81da-41f8-b5e3-ab1b8c94b748\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-90df06ee-3ac6-490f-a506-0e3ba2507bf1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-1aaecba7-32e8-48c6-aed9-b1b793546b67\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-06944fda-dfc3-4c8d-8322-8acc2d3beb11\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-d1f17a0e-decb-46ff-be50-c3c29a4de3b4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-467a3f7e-b759-41d8-964a-64c4412814b4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 소개는 자신의 얼굴을 노출하여 고객에게 강렬하게 각인시키고 싶으신 보험에 종사하고 계신 대표님입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-d5931a7c-a584-481e-8e4b-019a3524765c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c3546e16-c75b-4176-a813-3334aad4f1c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-3f29356d-b99c-4035-87e8-136584e01215\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-26f16c89-9636-4943-9700-b8ec1b52412e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-e7fd769d-877c-4825-820e-5ead70e9b78e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-586edb6f-1be7-48a9-b58c-a76303d56a67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-35c9ab7d-06ee-4ef5-ad3c-fdcf0005e598\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-84b477ba-60db-43d4-b124-64d5af832555\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음은 M사 보험 소속으로 영업중인 팀장님께서 의뢰하신 건입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-b8bf7d46-fa25-4e28-bd8f-9a4e50cd1989\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-88996548-9103-43be-80ea-a4516ca70c3f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">* 여기 디자인에 등장하는 모든 기록과 내용은 오혜경대표님의 동의를 얻어서 올려드리는것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af416cc8-0ba3-40f6-9b2f-ba159ab1b2e0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-59a614e0-1c86-48c0-9dd3-7620d70dcd08\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e7459515-23bf-4ff6-98f5-e4a26785153d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-318d543f-a083-4e25-b67e-d5afec820be3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-e8a5a0a6-0f96-4ac8-846e-fec388f8594f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-e5489305-bcab-4d2e-a8ab-de88d85ef260\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-50d48fff-ef18-433c-bdc3-4eee21fc9ad7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cea39073-4832-4e64-880a-00e5617c0c12\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함 진행</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-c020d8fb-d4d8-4078-86e0-cee7dc15b4f6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d083b0a1-8dc8-483f-9e5f-d085501a9dbe\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">작업의 진행은 다음과 같이 됩니다. 모두 참고하시고 주문접수해 주시기 바랍니다. 1차로 자료를 카톡으로 주셨습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-789e1509-fb50-45ad-94ef-44af98578ceb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-508e088c-6fab-4d12-90e0-1169a7b079f1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6034a799-009e-4734-bab5-db091049a660\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dc301aea-d34b-4062-80fb-9f6f259e2778\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0796976d-a76a-41d2-b493-a9b7f3bbe773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-aff301c3-0054-4f70-aab6-e366431f4427\" style=\"\">1차 카톡 요청</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8ddd46a1-aec7-4cf4-81f9-c3f0e75ffd0e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/003.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e24fc13-d205-4e2b-9539-f72ff9a165b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ea2bb15d-0897-42e3-a491-5fc8be2363e4\" style=\"\">프로필 사진 전송</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-afbcbab2-8745-454f-bdca-0c39ddc1fc98\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e36cc82f-7faa-4657-940f-87e6e449df6d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f5fbf405-13b6-4b26-a0b4-25ae364d0744\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이번에 작업하신 보험팀장님은 프로필 사진이 핸드폰으로 찍으신 거라 기존에 템플릿과 맞지 않아 작업템플릿을 추가해서 만들었습니다. 이번에 템플릿 추가로 프로필 사진이 마땅하지 않으신 분은 위와 같이 템플릿을 구성할 예정입니다. 제가 여러번 언급드렸지만 이 프로필명함의 가장 중요한 포인트는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-08155380-9291-4a63-bc18-2e0f836bf271\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>My Keyword</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e62a8dcd-efce-437a-9098-55e28a82e464\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">와</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b4c6c520-3ac1-4cab-ab75-246ba699eec1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b> 프로필 사진</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d7231585-9033-4e84-a7f6-5125c7c522ec\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">입니다. 프로필 사진이 없으신 분은 이참에 촬영을 권장드립니다. 마땅히 촬영하는 업체를 모르시면 저에게 문의주셔도 좋습니다. 가장 합리적인 금액에 헤어와 메이크업까지된 프로필 사진을 촬영하여 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-816c6fa1-09c6-4415-b40a-0c0aa4c2a965\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-29d70ead-a618-4aeb-b97b-d5b53ed4e296\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f4c84e3-ee7c-435e-bcd6-cfac779fe605\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/004.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0385048f-c7f8-4ee2-842a-0f5da572e302\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8306f5e7-0f2f-4c0d-993e-3d10ee04f00b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2f647a57-6c99-4f34-b42e-515a0e86d8d8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">1차로 두가지 컬러의 시안을 제출하였습니다. 기존의 템플릿과는 다른 템플릿을 만드느라 시간이 많이 소요되었습니다. 그래도 약 4시간만에 만들고 교정을 요청하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c85d8fd-1369-4c4f-8952-e6987439e690\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7e562c0b-a188-42b1-aec0-95c2803b5aa1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-collage\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-collage\" id=\"SE-ba3ac0f7-ac35-4b60-8fc2-522a1a9139be\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item se-imageGroup-col-2\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" id=\"SE-4a1ab433-8ab5-4d40-b1e5-3749d813f07c\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/005.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" id=\"SE-10205eec-23bb-439f-a99c-1df9b6e6e150\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/006.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5aa9bd9a-d884-460d-983f-b7b5a377f1e0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50360b21-e22a-4fef-80d4-83dc9356f06f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e462aba0-63b0-44b1-b38c-705e7b400136\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이렇게 교정작업을 카톡으로 진행하였습니다. 아주 간편하게 진행될 수 있어 서로의 커뮤니케이션을 중요하게 생각하는 저희와 캐미가 잘 맞았습니다. 서로의 교정을 주고 받는 것은 고객과의 호흡이 중요합니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 커뮤니케이션을 가장 중요하게 생각합니다. 이점에서 저희와 좋은 교감을 나눠주신 팀장님 고맙습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-deca0da9-51ac-48d7-aa0f-585be9365f5a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-741ba30b-7f93-447f-b930-d835a0c28bec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6f48e42e-48da-4a2b-af9a-773d520f12ff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3e4bb571-258b-4efc-96b6-ab067f073a01\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">약 6~7번의 교정을 주고 받고 (카톡으로 적어 주셔서 오타는 거의 없었습니다.) 마지막 최종 시안을 넘겨 드렸습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47092dcc-9d88-493d-8ac3-ee4c172eed2a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/007.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aa21fdcb-cdc8-432e-930b-6045de74feb0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9443036f-9a98-4343-9820-155e5489a3c7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1094cc19-57bc-4ce6-94c8-eb1c862e4efe\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">마지막에 팀장님의 직책이 빠져있는 것을 보고 저희가 최종 파일로 다시 한번 이미지를 만들어 드렸습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6bcfc968-c540-4437-8477-2a692be04047\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d9b06100-4a48-43c6-a159-431e934e84c3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">최종파일을 작업해서 고해상도 png파일로 전송하여 드리고 다른분께도 소개해 주신다는 말씀이 너무 감사했습니다. 열심히 하겠습니다. 많이 알려주시면 최선을 다해 소개에 피해가 가지 않도록 최선을 다하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07245b25-8d32-4b70-9853-3e6c2eff6ec4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b0c8d7cf-5024-495e-a9b3-b9ebdea1ee09\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-f669bf73-e494-451b-8fcd-01c1b67234b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b745e91-3c80-4359-b5b1-8a750745b1ac\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ba5b7b1c-0ce4-428c-a19c-a810a2e4cd96\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>프로필명함 : 자동차 세일즈 / 건강보조 판매</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2515f8e0-4c24-4cb6-adcd-d344cecf66bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-b691fb7f-a552-428a-b144-1dcb4e188c79\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bed51df2-a0f2-4971-9000-e4586b8566f3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222950085849/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5dd0d776-6890-4d6e-88e4-1a317ebd7ca4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-02b34987-694a-47d5-b044-9122b36cd159\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1c4fae29-2227-4a56-92dd-019c8790dc70\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음과 같은 디자인 시안은 영업의 일선에 계시는 자동차 판매 세일즈맨이나 다단계 또는 방문판매로 마케팅을 하시는 대표님을 위한 템플릿입니다. 다음회에는 갤러리와 전문직에 계시는 템플릿을 올려 드리겠습니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3a8ec01-312b-4709-b830-f99779163aee\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-365666ea-6ada-4b53-8730-31ca70db999f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4ce6957d-f4ad-4e36-bb97-0b4ce59aba31\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F222950085849#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}